title: Mythbusters S10E14 : The A To Z Of ExplosivesWebrip
description:
Get ready for one of the most explosive episodes in Mythbusters' history, as the team unveil their A to Z of explosions. This is the ultimate guide to everything that goes boom, as Adam, Jamie, Kari, Grant and Tory reminisce about their favourite explosions from the past. They kick things off with A for Audit where they do a monumental countdown of the history of the show's explosions where it's revealed that there have been 752 detonations and counting.
